Mr. Lin

590
00:37:33,280 --> 00:37:34,880
I'm really begging you.

591
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:37,240
No results,

592
00:37:37,240 --> 00:37:38,160
then get the hell out.

593
00:37:39,640 --> 00:37:42,360
This is a business, not a charity.

594
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:45,360
Get out.

595
00:37:45,560 --> 00:37:46,160
Out.

596
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:49,160
Lin Wenbin

597
00:37:49,160 --> 00:37:50,200
You bastard!

598
00:37:50,200 --> 00:37:51,080
What are you doing?

599
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:53,080
Let go of me!

600
00:37:53,080 --> 00:37:54,760
Are you trying to push me over the edge?

601
00:37:55,400 --> 00:37:57,120
Thirteen years at this company!

602
00:37:57,160 --> 00:37:58,360
Are you going to let me live or not?

603
00:37:58,360 --> 00:37:58,960
Let go of me!

604
00:37:58,960 --> 00:37:59,720
Lin Wenbin!

605
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,080
Lin Wenbin!

606
00:38:01,080 --> 00:38:02,360
Thirteen years!

607
00:38:02,360 --> 00:38:03,680
And you just kick me to the curb!

608
00:38:03,680 --> 00:38:05,280
You're leaving me with nothing!

609
00:38:05,400 --> 00:38:06,560
Lin Wenbin!

610
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:05,680
Take a look at the first-half numbers.

611
00:39:06,280 --> 00:39:07,560
They're nowhere near the target.

612
00:39:08,960 --> 00:39:10,640
If they don't improve in the second half,

613
00:39:14,080 --> 00:39:14,880
sorry to say,

614
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:15,960
sorry to say,

615
00:39:16,120 --> 00:39:17,360
especially certain people,

616
00:39:17,720 --> 00:39:19,040
who keep dragging everyone down.

617
00:39:19,840 --> 00:39:21,760
Wu Yuanfeng, you're staying for overtime.

618
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:53,600
This is yours.

619
00:39:55,680 --> 00:39:56,680
Hey, delivery guy.

620
00:39:58,080 --> 00:39:59,080
The box is broken.

621
00:39:59,560 --> 00:40:00,360
Thanks.

622
00:40:00,520 --> 00:40:01,080
It's fine, it's fine.

623
00:40:02,480 --> 00:40:04,280
Didn't you forget to call me last time?

624
00:40:04,280 --> 00:40:05,520
Let me make it up to you today.

625
00:40:50,560 --> 00:40:52,760
Even you two are picking on me

626
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:08,160
Fine

627
00:41:08,560 --> 00:41:09,760
I'll tell you then

628
00:41:10,920 --> 00:41:13,160
but you have to keep it a secret

629
00:41:13,360 --> 00:41:14,600
If you break your word

630
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:15,880
May lightning strike me.
